King, Carr, Franzen, Flynn.

64
00:04:07,289 --> 00:04:08,623
O ALIENISTA

65
00:04:08,707 --> 00:04:10,041
DESOSSAR UMA GALINHA

66
00:04:10,125 --> 00:04:12,127
